Class LinkedListGraph

java.lang.Object
AbstractGraph
LinkedListGraph
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph
public class LinkedListGraph
extends AbstractGraph
A LinkedListGraph is an extension of the AbstractGraph abstract class that uses an 2D LinkedList to represent the edges.
